XML/RSS/Tools version 0.06
==========================

RSS/RDF feeds are commonly available ways of distributing the latest news about a
given web site for news syndication. This module provides a VERY high level way of
manipulating them. You can easily use LWP, the XML::RSS and XML::LibXSLT do to this
yourself.

STATUS

Warning! this module is ALPHA code, it may have undocumented features "bugs", and
the API may change without notice. However it is currently under active development
and so now is the time to add features to the code base before the API becomes
fixed.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules for full functionality:

  XML::RSS XML::LibXSLT XML::LibXML LWP HTTP::GHTTP

